Title: Episode #5.7
Writer: Chris Ryan (based on the book by), Ed Whitmore, Richard Zajdlic
Actors: Philip Winchester, Sullivan Stapleton, Robson Green, Kay Lovelle
Plot: The team head for Vienna following the lead on Li-Na & Kwon. From Nina's agent they get details of a meeting between Kwon and someone from Locke's past. They observe the meeting but things do not go according to plan.
